  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities and duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for breakdown maintenance for all aircon &amp; electrical equipment</li>\n  <li>Manage repair and maintenance matters</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc duty as assigned</li>\n  <li>Assist to liaise and resolve problems with customers</li>\n  <li>Maintain good housekeeping and safety at site</li>\n  <li>Ensure that a high level of professionalism and customer service is maintained at all times</li>\n  <li>Possess some knowledge in using standard maintenance tools is preferred but not compulsory as training shall be provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Nitec/TVET/SKM1 to 3 in Mechanical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>A least 2 years of working experience in the related mechanical field</li>\n  <li>Able to start work immediately or within a short notice</li>\n  <li>Class 2B with own motorcycle would be added advantage</li>\n</ul>",
